Package com.example.webjson

Class StackQuery

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.example.webjson.StackQuery
  • public class StackQuery
extends java.lang.Object
    The StackQuery class allows you to send a custom query string to StackOverflow and obtain a list of ResultData objects back, with information about Java questions that match your query.

    You can customize the order of your results with the setSortBy(SortBy) and setSortOrder(SortOrder) methods. - Project Description - - Class Description - Author: Baber Arjumand Date: Aug 01 2019 Time: 11:26 PM
